Memo for the build system rewrite
=================================

Feature triggers
----------------

1. Extract detection code, taking care of prerequisites.
2. Remove detection code from connector.
3. Update options.conf.
4. Update testfarm.conf.
5. Update CPP options.
6. Update configure.ac.
7. Update doc/build/config-template.ac.
8. Update build examples.
9. Have the new file versioned.

